high_descs: Go straight for a few steps then turn right towards the fridge
Take a potato out of the fridge
Turn around and go as far as the table, then turn right and go to the sink, then turn right and go to the microwave
Microwave the potato then take it out of the microwave
Turn right and go to the table next to the stool
Put the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato on the kitchen table

high_descs: Move to the right facing the grey fridge
Remove the potato from inside of the fridge then shut the door
Carry the potato over to the the microwave directly to the left of the fridge
Place the potato inside of the microwave, turn it on then remove the potato
Carry the potato to the silver table top
Place the potato on the table to the left of the red fruit
anns.task_desc: Move a heated potato to the table

high_descs: Move forward and then turn to your right to face the fridge
Open the fridge door and pick up a potato from the shelf
Turn around and maneuver to your left so that you are facing the microwave and the fridge
Put the potato in the microwave, cook it for a few seconds and then take it back out
Move to your right and end up turning to face the kitchen table
Place the potato on the table
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato and set it on the table
